        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "A city in the tribe of Asher; which, it is probable, was one of those that Ben-hadad’s father had taken from the king of Israel, (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 20:34",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ",) not far from which was the plain of Galilee, where he intended to fight. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And the children of Israel went against them — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Being encouraged by the remembrance of their former success, and an expectation of assistance from God. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And pitched before them — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Probably upon some hilly ground where they might secure themselves, and watch for advantage against their enemies; which might be the reason why the Syrians durst not assault them before the seventh day, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 20:29",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Like two little flocks of kids — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Few and weak; being also, for convenience of fighting, and that they might seem more than they were, divided into two bodies.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
